  "A school cafeteria wastes 30% of its food daily. Students propose three solutions: composting food scraps, buying from local farms to reduce spoilage, and adjusting portion sizes based on actual consumption data. How do these solutions relate to the food waste hierarchy?": "",
  "Composting is the best solution because it turns all waste into a useful product": "",
