  "IPM has no advantages over conventional pesticide application": "",
  "IPM only saves money but has no environmental benefits": "",
  "The IPM approach maintains ecological balance by preserving beneficial predator insects, reduces chemical contamination of water and soil, prevents the development of pesticide-resistant pest populations, and lowers costs while achieving effective pest control.": "",
  "A city surrounded by farmland notices its tap water contains high nitrate levels, traced to fertilizer runoff from upstream farms. The farms use conventional practices with heavy synthetic fertilizer application. Downstream, the river feeding into a bay has created a dead zone. If the farms transitioned to precision agriculture, what specific improvements would be expected?": "",
