  "Aquaponics produces only ornamental plants, not food crops": "",
  "Aquaponics is ideal for space-limited urban settings because it requires no soil, recirculates water (using up to 90% less than field agriculture), can operate indoors with artificial lighting, and produces both protein (fish) and vegetables in a compact integrated system.": "",
  "A developing country relies heavily on monoculture coffee production for export income. A drought followed by a pest outbreak devastates the harvest, leaving farmers with no income and communities without food. An agricultural advisor recommends transitioning to agroforestry. How would agroforestry address the multiple vulnerabilities exposed by this crisis?": "",
