  "A government is considering two agricultural policies: Policy A subsidizes synthetic fertilizer purchases, keeping food prices low. Policy B provides incentives for cover crops, crop rotation, and reduced fertilizer use, but food prices may increase slightly in the short term. Using a sustainability framework, which policy better serves long-term food security?": "",
